	   <tr><td colspan=2>Depends on race...<br>As an Erudite there really is no better way to spend them then what you feel you want to get a head start in. Your attack skills, spell skills and stuff like that will increase to level max within a 5 fight span... Havent reached the level to start researching yet, but that might be worth saving up for.<br>Languages? Whenever you group with someone with a language you dont have, just make them send you a few group says till you increase it a few steps, then its just up to you to find someone who wants to learn the language too... Preferably about the same int as you so you advance together. The good thing is you can always teach your comrades to one level higher then yourself which means that if there are 2 of you you could start with having just 1 point in a language and given enough work you will both master it at the end of the day.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
